extends ../layout

block content
  .row
    .col-xs-4.item-photo
      img(style='max-width:100%;', src='https://ak1.ostkcdn.com/images/products/8818677/Samsung-Galaxy-S4-I337-16GB-AT-T-Unlocked-GSM-Android-Cell-Phone-85e3430e-6981-4252-a984-245862302c78_600.jpg')
    .col-xs-5(style='border:0px solid gray')
      // Datos del vendedor y titulo del producto
      h3 Samsung Galaxy S4 I337 16GB 4G LTE Unlocked GSM Android Cell Phone
      h5(style='color:#337ab7')
        | vendido por
        a(href='#') Samsung
        |  ·
        small(style='color:#337ab7') (5054 ventas)
      // Precios
      h6.title-price
        small PRECIO OFERTA
      h3(style='margin-top:0px;') U$S 399
      // Detalles especificos del producto
      .section
        h6.title-attr(style='margin-top:15px;')
          small COLOR
        div
          .attr(style='width:25px;background:#5a5a5a;')
          .attr(style='width:25px;background:white;')
      .section(style='padding-bottom:5px;')
        h6.title-attr
          small CAPACIDAD
        div
          .attr2 16 GB
          .attr2 32 GB
      .section(style='padding-bottom:20px;')
        h6.title-attr
          small CANTIDAD
        div
          .btn-minus
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-minus
          input(value='1')
          .btn-plus
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-plus
      // Botones de compra
      .section(style='padding-bottom:20px;')
        button.btn.btn-success
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-shopping-cart(style='margin-right:20px', aria-hidden='true')
          |  Agregar al carro
        h6
          a(href='#')
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-heart-empty(style='cursor:pointer;')
            |  Agregar a lista de deseos
    .col-xs-9
      ul.menu-items
        li.active Detalle del producto
        li Garantía
        li Vendedor
        li Envío
      div(style='width:100%;border-top:1px solid silver')
        p(style='padding:15px;')
          small
            | Stay connected either on the phone or the Web with the Galaxy S4 I337 from Samsung. With 16 GB of memory and a 4G connection, this phone stores precious photos and video and lets you upload them to a cloud or social network at blinding-fast speed. With a 17-hour operating life from one charge, this phone allows you keep in touch even on the go.
            | With its built-in photo editor, the Galaxy S4 allows you to edit photos with the touch of a finger, eliminating extraneous background items. Usable with most carriers, this smartphone is the perfect companion for work or entertainment.
        small
          ul
            li Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen display with 16M colors
            li Available on GSM, AT T, T-Mobile and other carriers
            li
              | Compatible with GSM 850 / 900 / 1800; HSDPA 850 / 1900 / 2100 LTE; 700 MHz Class 17 / 1700 / 2100 networks
            li MicroUSB and USB connectivity
            li Interfaces with Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual band and Bluetooth
            li Wi-Fi hotspot to keep other devices online when a connection is not available
            li SMS, MMS, email, Push Mail, IM and RSS messaging
            li
              | Front-facing camera features autofocus, an LED flash, dual video call capability and a sharp 4128 x 3096 pixel picture
            li Features 16 GB memory and 2 GB RAM
            li Upgradeable Jelly Bean v4.2.2 to Jelly Bean v4.3 Android OS
            li 17 hours of talk time, 350 hours standby time on one charge
            li Available in white or black
            li Model I337
            li Package includes phone, charger, battery and user manual
            li
              | Phone is 5.38 inches high x 2.75 inches wide x 0.13 inches deep and weighs a mere 4.59 oz